				<div class="tfdv">
					<button class="btn">檔案上傳</button>
					<em>ex.企劃PPT；檔案格式 .ppt / .doc / .pdf/ .zip</em>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="tfth col-md-3"><span>雲端資料夾網址</span></div>
			<div class="tftd col-md-9">
				<input type="text" placeholder="請直接貼入網址"><br>
				<input type="text" placeholder="請直接貼入網址"><br>
				<input type="text" placeholder="請直接貼入網址"><br>
			</div>
			<div class="tfth col-md-3"><span>是否加購PPM</span></div>
			<div class="tftd col-md-9">
				<label for="" class="sp"><input type="radio" name="radio"><span class="radiomark"></span> 是</label>
				<label for="" class="sp"><input type="radio" name="radio"><span class="radiomark"></span> 否</label>

				<em>PPM為拍攝元素細節再次確認服務，並擁有更換一次素材的權利；一旦確認勾選，將自動於尾款金額加價$3,000。</em>
			</div>
			<div class="tfth col-md-3"><span>其他備註資訊</span></div>
			<div class="tftd col-md-9">
				<textarea name="" id="" cols="" rows="5"></textarea>
			</div>

		</div>
		<div class="btns center">
			<button class="btn" type="submit" name="action" value="save">儲存</button>
			<button class="btn btnIm" type="submit" name="action" value="submit">確認提交</button>
		</div>
	</form>
</div>
